Developer Terms of Use
des:
We are a community minded internet radio station based in South Australia whose main focus is to raise funds for people in South Australia who are in need.

This is done through our Rossco Media

All monies raised through our various initiatives are raised for South Australians, by South Australians

CRA is also passionate about promoting the local creative arts be it singers, songwriters, musicians, bands and other performing artists that would benefit from being promoted on radio.
